OL,3,CFundraising TfL worker recognised with
OL,4,CBEM in New Year Honours list
OL,6,FA Transport for London worker, who has
OL,7,Fspent the last decade raising tens of
OL,8,Fthousands of pounds for various causes
OL,9,Fin the capital, has been awarded a
OL,10,FBritish Empire Medal (BEM) for
OL,11,Fcharitable service.
OL,13,FLeon Hall, 52, began his ten year
OL,14,Fcampaign when his close friend and TfL
OL,15,Fcolleague, Steve Lloyd, was diagnosed
OL,16,Fwith an aggressive brain tumour in
OL,17,F2014.
