OL,3,CFundraising TfL worker recognised with
OL,4,CBEM in New Year Honours list
OL,6,FIn support of his friend, Mr Hall
OL,7,Forganised a fundraising event for the
OL,8,FBrain Tumour Research charity the
OL,9,Ffollowing year.
OL,11,FHe enlisted a group of colleagues to
OL,12,Fcycle the length of the District Line,
OL,13,Fraising #30,000.
OL,15,FMr Lloyd passed away at the end of
OL,16,F2015 at the age of 39 as a result of
OL,17,Fhis illness.
OL,19,FIn his memory, Mr Hall took on The One
OL,20,FLondon Charity Cycle Challenge in 2016
OL,21,Fand raised a further #30,000.
