OL,6,FThe combined total of over #60,000 is
OL,7,Fthe equivalent of funding almost 22
OL,8,Fdays of research in the charity's
OL,9,Fbrain tumour research centres.
OL,11,FMr Hall said he took "great pride" in
OL,12,Fcoordinating the events.
OL,14,F"We had a lot of fun doing it, but
OL,15,Fagain, we made a difference. We helped
OL,16,Fto raise awareness and raise funds,
OL,17,Fwhich is vital for trying to find a
OL,18,Fcure for such a terrible disease," he
OL,19,Fsaid.
