OL,4,CBEM in New Year Honours list
OL,6,FThe north London resident has also
OL,7,Fdevoted time to community projects
OL,8,Fover the years, notably installing a
OL,9,Freal underground train carriage in the
OL,10,Fplayground of a local primary school,
OL,11,Fwhich serves as a library.
OL,13,FHe said it was a "rewarding"
OL,14,Fexperience: "I was just amazed by
OL,15,Flooking at the faces of the children
OL,16,Fwhen they actually saw what was
OL,17,Fdelivered to them ... they were like,
OL,18,Fwow, this is amazing.
