OL,6,F"It's a real railway carriage that's
OL,7,Fin their school that they can actually
OL,8,Fplay with and use for educational
OL,9,Fpurposes. It's really good to see."
OL,11,FTen years on from his original
OL,12,Ffundraising event, Mr Hall he said he
OL,13,Fwas "overwhelmed" to hear that he had
OL,14,Fbeen named in the King's New Year
OL,15,FHonours list.
OL,17,F"I can't put it into words, really.
OL,18,FI'm still getting it into my head ...
OL,19,FIt was a pleasant surprise and a bit
OL,20,Fof a shock when it actually happened,"
OL,21,Fhe said.
