OL,6,FDescribing the moment he received the
OL,7,Fletter, he added: "Got home from work
OL,8,Fand there was a very official
OL,9,Fgovernment letter that was on the
OL,10,Ftable.
OL,12,F"I didn't know whether it was a court
OL,13,Fsummons or if I'd been written to by Q
OL,14,For James Bond or something."
OL,16,FMr Hall will receive his medal later
OL,17,Fthis year.
